      "writtenOn": "2016-12-06T23:51:19Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "You did better at me than hunting that down, thanks!\n\nUpdated to return a built-up one rather than a magic blob.\n\n... Though looking at it now, it\u0027s not exactly what one might describe as non-magic either. :) But at least by using winnt.h it points at some documentation.",
      "parentUuid": "ed7c572f_4c2effa3",
